;; This implements very simple, yet functional WikiWikiWeb.
;;
;; This program uses 'login-manager' application server for
;; user authentication handling.

;; Uncomment one of the followings if you want to try
;; DBI-backed storage.  Note that you might need settings
;; on the DBMS server side as well.
;(primary-database-name "mysql:kahua::db=test")
